criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:  The demonstration sites are:

  -  Contra Costa County, Calif.;

  -  Miami-Dade County, Fla.;

  -  Palm Beach County, Fla.;

  -  Rockdale County, Ga.;

  -  Winnebago County, Ill.;

  -  Boston, MA;

  -  Brooklyn, N.Y.;

  -  Westchester County, N.Y.;

  -  Pitt County, N.C.;

  -  Cuyahoga County, Ohio;

  -  North Charleston, S.C.;

  -  Rutland, Vt.

       -  After the 12-month assessment phase, up to six of the demonstration sites will
          be selected to continue a three-year implementation phase.
